43:02.080 --> 43:04.549
EDDIE:
The rage starts to build,

43:04.582 --> 43:06.551
and it needs an outlet.

43:06.584 --> 43:10.055
So what happens
when we let it take over?

43:10.088 --> 43:13.491
Do we regain control
by unleashing our fury?

43:15.260 --> 43:18.163
Or have we crossed a line
we can't come back from?

